==事件==
[[File:BRICS_leaders_in_Brazil.jpeg|thumb]]
巴西总统[[迪尔玛·罗塞夫|迪尔玛·罗塞夫]]邀请金砖国家领导人前去观看[[2014年世界杯足球赛决赛|2014年世界杯足球赛决赛]]。印度总理莫迪回应：“体育向世界各国传递友好精神和归属感，或许国际足联世界杯成为连接各国的桥梁<ref>{{cite web |author=IANS |url=http://www.indiawest.com/news/india/article_7620d1de-f600-11e3-9dc2-001a4bcf887a.html |title=Modi Likely to Watch FIFA World Cup Final ahead of BRICS Summit - India West: News |publisher=India West |date=2014-06-17 |accessdate=2014-07-16 |archive-date=2016-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303174254/http://www.indiawest.com/news/india/article_7620d1de-f600-11e3-9dc2-001a4bcf887a.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>！”

==议程==
[[金砖国家开发银行|金砖国家开发银行]]宣告成立<ref>{{cite web |url=http://larouchepac.com/node/31248 |title=On Eve of BRICS Summit, Atlantic Nations Push Green Death, Pacific Pushes Development |publisher=Larouchepac.com |date=2014-07-08 |accessdate=2014-07-16 |archive-date=2014-07-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714162635/http://larouchepac.com/node/31248 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。7月15日，组织签订了一份花1000亿美元建立开发银行，另用1000亿美元作储备资金的协议，同时签署了金砖国家出口信贷机构和创新合作协议文件<ref>{{cite web |url=http://rt.com/business/173008-brics-bank-currency-pool/ |title=BRICS establish $100bn bank and currency reserves to cut out Western dominance — RT Business |publisher=Rt.com |date= |accessdate=2014-07-16 |archive-date=2014-07-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140716015223/http://rt.com/business/173008-brics-bank-currency-pool/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。该组织的一份新闻稿写道：“我们仍对[[国际货币基金组织|国际货币基金组织]]未能执行2010年改革感到失望，表示严重关切，这可能会对IMF的合法性、可信度和有效性产生负面影响<ref>{{cite web |url=http://brics6.itamaraty.gov.br/media2/press-releases |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-07-17 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140718154506/http://brics6.itamaraty.gov.br/media2/press-releases |archivedate=2014-07-18 }}</ref>。”同时将国际货币基金组织和[[世界银行|世界银行]]视为对手<ref>{{cite web |url=http://rt.com/business/171500-russia-2bn-brics-bank/ |title=BRICS countries near development bank deal to rival IMF, WB — RT Business |publisher=Rt.com |date= |accessdate=2014-07-16 |archive-date=2014-07-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140715180635/http://rt.com/business/171500-russia-2bn-brics-bank/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
===反响===
俄罗斯总统[[普京|普京]]表示，本次峰会旨在消除美元依赖，加强国际法治<ref>{{cite web |author=Published time: July 15, 2014 02:38 |url=http://rt.com/politics/official-word/172768-putin-brics-economies-alliance/ |title=Putin: No plans for BRICS military, political alliance — RT Russian politics |publisher=Rt.com |date= |accessdate=2014-07-16 |archive-date=2014-07-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140717190150/http://rt.com/politics/official-word/172768-putin-brics-economies-alliance/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>：
<blockquote>在金砖国家里，我们看到了一整套与战略利益相吻合的措施。首先，改革国际货币和金融体系是各国共同意愿。目前的形势对金砖国家尤其是广大新兴经济体不利，我们应更为积极地参与IMF和世界银行的决策系统。国际货币体系本身在很大程度上[[布雷顿森林体系|取决于美元]]，准确地说，是美国当局的货币和金融政策。金砖国家就要改变这一点。</blockquote>

===金砖国家-南美洲国家联盟峰会===
金砖国家定于7月16日在[[巴西利亚|巴西利亚]]与[[南美洲国家联盟|南美洲国家联盟]]领导人会晤<ref>{{cite web|title=Los líderes del BRICS, Unasur, Cuba, México y Costa Rica se citan en Brasilia|url=http://www.lavanguardia.com/economia/20140715/54411930114/los-lideres-del-brics-unasur-cuba-mexico-y-costa-rica-se-citan-en-brasilia.html|website=LaVanguardia.com|publisher=LaVanguardia|accessdate=2014-07-15|archive-date=2017-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170630122604/http://www.lavanguardia.com/economia/20140715/54411930114/los-lideres-del-brics-unasur-cuba-mexico-y-costa-rica-se-citan-en-brasilia.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

